{"tid":2183373,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"華為停止贊助澳洲欖球隊 稱澳洲營商環境負面","createTime":"2020-09-01T02:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T07:12:08.000Z","uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98faf501b998c693485a9a370822cefd5926dfa2","tid":2183373,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:01:07.000Z","msg":"中國電訊設備商華為遭美國為首英語國家封殺，澳洲也在此列，加上中國澳洲關係近期轉差之際，華為宣佈停止贊助澳洲欖球隊「坎培拉奇襲者」（Canberra Raiders），結束雙方9年合作關係。華為亦指，澳洲營商環境「持續負面」。<br />\n<br />\n華為在澳洲子企業周一（31日）發表聲明，宣佈提前1年解除對坎培拉奇襲者的贊助合約。坎培拉奇襲者是澳洲全國欖球聯賽（National Rugby League，NRL）的隊伍，該隊與華為合約原定2021年賽季結束時才到期。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2735000/2739906/crhw2_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2735000%2F2739906%2Fcrhw2_600.jpeg&h=ae309a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2739906/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E8%B4%8A%E5%8A%A9%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%AC%96%E7%90%83%E9%9A%8A%20%E7%A8%B1%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2739906%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E8%25B4%258A%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%25AC%2596%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%259A%258A%2520%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%259D%25A2&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7hSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=c7b9c148\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2739906/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E8%B4%8A%E5%8A%A9%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%AC%96%E7%90%83%E9%9A%8A%20%E7%A8%B1%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2</a>"},{"pid":"1ed53c80a1740b03aa59518c35f57ccfb401481c","tid":2183373,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi